'''Inuktitut''' ta un lenga papiá na nort di [[Canada]]. E ta papiá den tur areanan nort di e [[tree line]], inclui partinan di e provinsianan di [[Newfoundland and Labrador]], [[Quebec]], to some extent in northeastern Manitoba as well as the Northwest Territories and Nunavut. It is one of the aboriginal languages written with Canadian Aboriginal syllabics.
